column16: Dodgers challenged (play at 1st), call on the field was overturned: Carl Crawford singles on a ground ball to shortstop Matt Duffy.   Yasiel Puig scores.    Joc Pederson to 3rd.    Hanley Ramirez to 2nd.
Hanley Ramirez singles on a line drive to center fielder Gary Brown.   Yasiel Puig to 3rd.    Joc Pederson to 2nd.
Adrian Gonzalez grounds out, second baseman Joe Panik to first baseman Travis Ishikawa.   Yasiel Puig to 2nd.
Yasiel Puig singles on a ground ball to shortstop Matt Duffy.  Dee Gordon out at 3rd, shortstop Matt Duffy to second baseman Joe Panik.
Dee Gordon reaches on a fielding error by shortstop Matt Duffy.
Zack Greinke homers (1) on a fly ball to left center field.   A.  J.   Ellis scores.
A.  J.   Ellis singles on a line drive to center fielder Gary Brown.
Juan Uribe grounds into a force out, fielded by shortstop Brandon Crawford.   Carl Crawford out at 2nd.
Carl Crawford reaches on a fielding error by second baseman Joe Panik.   Hanley Ramirez to 2nd.
Hanley Ramirez singles on a ground ball to shortstop Brandon Crawford.
Adrian Gonzalez lines out to center fielder Juan Perez.
Corey Dickerson singles on a line drive to center fielder Angel Pagan.   Drew Stubbs scores.    Corey Dickerson to 2nd on the throw.
Drew Stubbs grounds into a force out, pitcher Mike Kickham to second baseman Joe Panik.   Justin Morneau out at 2nd.    Drew Stubbs to 1st.
Justin Morneau singles on a line drive to right fielder Hunter Pence.
